# Setup

In repository root:
`git submodule init && git submodule update`

Then:
```
# Install system deps
sudo apt-get install python-twisted python-openssl make openjdk-6-jre

# Install YUI compressor somewhere and make strophejs
cd Chat/vendor/strophejs
YUI_COMPRESSOR=/path/to/yui.jar make

# Build and install deps
cd Chat/vendor/punjab
python setup.py build
sudo python setup.py install

# Start service
sudo a2enmod proxy_http
sudo service apache2 restart
sudo twistd punjab
```
